Docs.remarks:
            The token object needs to be formatted depending on the specific provider. These are some
            examples of formats based on the providers:

MicrosoftAccount{"authenticationToken":"<the_authentication_token>"}
Facebook{"access_token":"<the_access_token>"}
Google{"access_token":"<the_access_token>"}

